🌍 Explore Beyond Borders: ISME Seminar on Opportunities in Studying Abroad 🎓

Our recent seminar on 'Opportunities in Studying Abroad' was nothing short of enlightening! 🌟

Ms. Bhavna Jaggi, a seasoned expert with 10 years of experience as Manager and senior counselor at Overseas Education, graced us with her knowledge and insights into the world of international education. 📚

In an engaging 1.5-hour session, students were introduced to a plethora of opportunities awaiting them overseas. From the importance of overseas education with Satguru Overseas Education to the range of services offered throughout the academic journey, the seminar covered it all! 🌟

Key highlights included learning about partner universities and institutions, the robust support system for students, inspiring success stories, and invaluable scholarship opportunities. 💼

Satguru Overseas Education, with their comprehensive services including career counseling, admission assistance, visa processing, accommodation, and pre-departure support, are truly shaping the dreams of aspiring students. 🌟

Their expertise in guiding students towards the right university selections has established them as a trusted resource in the field of overseas education. 🎓

Thank you, Ms. Bhavna Jaggi, and Satguru Overseas Education, for empowering our students to embark on their global academic journeys! 🌏

✈️ Exploring the Skies: ISME Seminar on Career Opportunities in Aviation 🛩️

We had an incredible seminar on 'Career Opportunities in Aviation' organized by ISME, featuring a panel of distinguished speakers who shared invaluable insights into the world of aviation. 🌟

From Ms. Shloka Hajare, Head of Operations at Skyforce Innovations Pvt. Ltd., to Dev Shah, founder and CEO of Skyforce Innovations Private Limited, and many more esteemed guests, the session was packed with expertise and inspiration. 💼

Mr. Manmohan Chawla, Vice Chairman of the Aeronautical Society of India - Mumbai, and Ashwani Sharma, University Professor and Adviser, shed light on exciting career paths in the aviation industry. 🌐

The seminar, spanning an engaging 1.5 hours, left our students captivated and eager to soar to new heights in their careers. ✨

Special thanks to the Aeronautical Society of India Mumbai Branch for their dedication to nurturing future aviation professionals through outreach programs. 🙌

And the cherry on top? A thrilling display of drone technology, giving us a glimpse into the future of aviation innovation! 🚁

Stay tuned for more enriching experiences with ISME!
